Code: EXEC SQL SELECT DISTINCT NUM_APOL_SINISTRO, COUNT(*) FROM seguros.v0sini_lanclote1 WHERE FONTE = :FONTE AND NUM_LOTE = :NUM_LOTE AND OPERACAO BETWEEN 3000 AND 3999 AND ((NUM_APOL_SINISTRO BETWEEN 0103100000000 AND 0103199999999) OR (NUM_APOL_SINISTRO BETWEEN 0105300000000 AND 0105399999999)) GROUP BY NUM_APOL_SINISTRO HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY NUM_APOL_SINISTRO END SQL
